# provided by portage's packages or similar. In order:
# - Archiving tools, provided by their own ebuilds
# - ncurses stuff
# - less stuff
# - bind utils
# - rsh stuff
# - binutils gprof
# - dc stuff
# and the rest are misc utils we already provide somewhere else.
